Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.78,0:08:06.76,main,,0,0,0,,御风术
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.86,0:08:09.73,main,,0,0,0,,基修
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.00,0:08:22.83,main,,0,0,0,,这东西已经没用了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.13,0:08:24.37,main,,0,0,0,,去跟大家汇合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.63,0:08:26.16,main,,0,0,0,,Fire Ball
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.51,0:08:28.54,main,,0,0,0,,赶紧换地儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.85,0:08:42.18,main,,0,0,0,,蒂法 古代龙盯上的是我们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.48,0:08:43.81,main,,0,0,0,,必须离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.98,0:08:44.69,main,,0,0,0,,好 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.19,0:08:46.65,main,,0,0,0,,伊露库库 麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.03,0:08:48.31,main,,0,0,0,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.13,0:09:06.04,main,,0,0,0,,谢谢啦
